Desk Calendars

Keep your days, weeks and months at your fingertips with our desk calendars, which help organise your time while keeping your desk tidy. Hand them out to colleagues in the office or give them to customers in shops or at trade shows.

  • Five sizes to choose from
  • 4 models

Find out how to dispose of this material correctly - Explore

Custom Table Calendars 2024

If you're looking for a way to imprint your logo in the minds of customers, what better way to do it than with a custom desk calendar? With a desk calendar, you can be present on your customers' desks for a whole year, and not in a passive way but with a useful object they will interact with daily.

By giving a desk calendar as a gift, success for your company is assured, as nothing is more welcome than something useful.

So what are you waiting for? Personalize one of our many templates in just a few simple steps and order your personalized desk calendars now!

Your Personalized Desk Calendars with Pixartprinting: Create Desk Calendars with Your Custom Graphics!

The Desk Calendar is an essential item for those who like to keep track of their commitments at any time during work. Despite the advent of technological alternatives, having a calendar at hand to jot down appointments still makes a difference and allows for better organization.

If you are looking for the serenity of a reliable and high-quality partner for your customized Desk Calendar printing, Pixartprinting is the right choice for you! We offer a wide range of products that will surely meet your needs thanks to the variety of formats and the different pre-designed proposals available in the catalog. You will have the opportunity to customize the calendars with your custom graphics, aligning them with your company's coordinated image. You will have a tool with your colors and company logo to display on the desk, impressing collaborators and clients.

Print Custom Desk Calendars: Formats and Layouts

The customization of your Desk Calendars on our website is very simple and intuitive.

First, choose the format you prefer, among the available options:

  • 14.8 x 10.5 cm
  • 21 x 10.5 cm
  • 29.7 x 10.5 cm
  • 21 x 14.8 cm
  • 14.8 x 14.8 cm

Then select the layout you like best among the 3 possible alternatives. Keep in mind that there are no limits to layout customization! Just make sure that the dimensions, orientation, and number of pages are respected in setting up the file.

The calendar includes 28 pages (including the cover) on 250gsm matte coated paper, which is aging-resistant and enhances the definition and colors of images and texts. It also comes with support cardboard to ensure balance and stability.

Our Desk Calendar is affordable yet of high quality. It will host your personalized graphics, adding brilliance to their colors. So why wait? Order your Personalized Calendars now and equip your desk with a highly useful item, never again risking to forget any commitment!

Punctuality and Convenience at Your Fingertips: Order Your Custom Desk Calendars!

Ordering Desk Calendars on our website is a breeze. You can do it with just a few clicks and great ease. Simply select the customization options you prefer, then upload the file with your graphics. Once the purchase is completed, you will receive the product directly at your office with fast and punctual deliveries. This way, you'll avoid unnecessary waste of time, which you can use instead for your daily work activities.

Calendar and Mug: The Perfect Kit for an Office Gift Idea!

Looking for a gift idea for your colleagues, employees, or clients? A personalized desk calendar can be an excellent choice, but why not combine it with other products, creating a gift kit for the office?

Pair your desk calendar with a personalized mug, an diaries, or even a personalized pen, and create your office gift kit. Nothing is more appreciated than a useful item for daily use, and if you decide to use these items as promotional material, you'll ensure that potential customers always have your logo in front of them during their work activities.

Decide what to pair with your personalized desk calendars by choosing from the many products in our catalog dedicated to customized promotional items!

Custom Desk Calendars Made for You: Download the Useful Template

For the correct setup of your print file, we recommend downloading our useful Template from the page, after selecting your preferred configuration options. Inside the Template, you will find instructions from our graphic designers, which will help you achieve the best possible printing result: high-definition desk calendars that fully meet your expectations.

Company Desk Calendars in Line with Your Corporate Image

Pixartprinting is the ideal printing partner for creating personalized products that respect your company or association's corporate image. Not only company desk calendars, but also pens, pencils, and other stationery items that can be customized to give your office a unique appearance!

You can use your new personalized products for your daily work activities or to create original corporate gifts for partners and clients.
